README.md

    awesome emails

   [https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome]Awesome

     A collection of awesome frameworks, templates, tools, workflows and
     many more to build better emails.

Table of Contents

     * Frameworks
     * Cheatsheets
     * Templates
     * Tools
     * Services
     * Self-Hosted Services
     * Workflows
     * Articles
     * Inspirations
     * Statistics
     * Design
     * Testing
     * Learning

Frameworks

     * [https://mjml.io/]MJML - MJML is a markup language designed to
       reduce the pain of coding a responsive email. ¥
     * [https://github.com/zurb/foundation-emails]Foundation for Emails -
       Quickly create responsive HTML emails that work on any device &
       client. Even Outlook.
     * [http://emailframe.work/]Email Framework - The HTML email framework
       developed to help you build responsive HTML email.
     * [https://heml.io/]HEML - HEML is an open source markup language for
       building responsive email.

Cheatsheets

     * [https://devhints.io/html-email]Rico's cheatsheet - Rico's
       cheatsheet for HTML email

Templates

     * [https://github.com/bevacqua/campaign]Campaign - Compose responsive
       email templates easily, fill them with models, and send them out.
     * [https://www.sendwithus.com/resources/templates]Sendwithus - Open
       Source Email Templates
     * [https://github.com/mailchimp/Email-Blueprints]Mailchimp Email
       Blueprints - Email Blueprints is a collection of HTML email
       templates that can serve as a solid foundation and starting point
       for the design of emails.
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/email-templates/]Campaign Monitor
       Templates - Easily create beautiful, branded email marketing
       campaigns.
     * [https://github.com/mailgun/transactional-email-templates]Responsiv
       e Transactional HTML Email Templates (Each template is responsive
       and each has been tested in all the popular email clients.)
     * [https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus]Cerberus - Few responsive
       email patterns.
     * [https://github.com/internations/antwort]Antwort - Antwort offers
       responsive layouts for Email that both fits and adapts to client
       widths.
     * [https://github.com/charlesmudy/responsive-html-email-template]Resp
       onsive HTML Template - This template is designed to work on all
       major email platforms and it is built with media query, making it
       responsive for smartphones that supports media query.
     * [https://litmus.com/resources/free-responsive-email-templates/]Free
       Responsive template : Slate - Five pre-tested templates that work
       with any mailing service
     * [https://github.com/dwightjack/grunt-email-boilerplate]Grunt Email
       Boilerplate - A Grunt template to create emails.
     * [http://responsiveemailpatterns.com/]Responsive Email Patterns - A
       collection of patterns & modules for responsive emails.
     * [https://github.com/seanpowell/Email-Boilerplate]Email boilerplate
       - The email boilerplate for sending out nicely formatted messages.
     * [https://htmlemail.io/]htmlemail - Responsive HTML email templates
       for startups & developers.

Tools

     * [https://topol.io/]Topol - Create stunning responsive HTML e-mails
       in a minute.
     * [https://mjmlio.github.io/mjml-app/]MJML App - MJML official
       desktop app.
     * [http://freshinbox.com/tools/rollover/]Rollover - Generates code
       for a Rollover Image that displays an alternative image when the
       email recipient hovers the cursor over the image.
     * [http://buttons.cm/]Bulletproof Email Buttons - Design gorgeous
       buttons using progressively enhanced VML and CSS.
     * [http://backgrounds.cm/]Bulletproof Background Images - Use
       rock-solid background images in your HTML email with some help from

   VML and CSS.
     * [http://zurb.com/playground/testsubject]TestSubject - Test How Your
       Email Subject Lines Appear On The Most Popular Mobile Devices.
     * [https://mailspice.com/]mailspice analytics - Email analytics
       add-on for all email services that provides deep insights into all
       of your email campaigns (works with all ESPs).

Services

     * [https://mailchimp.com/]Mailchimp - MailChimp provides email
       marketing for more than 15 million people globally.
     * [https://mailjet.com/]Mailjet - all-in-one Email Services Provider
       that allows businesses to send Marketing, Transaction Email and
       Email Automation.
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/]Campaign monitor - Campaign
       Monitor makes it easy for you to create, send, and optimize your
       email marketing campaigns.
     * [https://sendgrid.com/]Sendgrid - Delivering your transactional and
       marketing email through one reliable platform.
     * [https://github.com/atech/postal]Postal - A fully featured open
       source mail delivery platform for incoming & outgoing e-mail.
     * [https://formcarry.com/]Formcarry - A form endpoint service with
       Zapier integration and file upload, no back-end skill required.
     * [https://formspree.io/]Formspree - A form endpoint service, totally
       free it forwards incoming submissions to your email.
     * [https://www.sparkpost.com/]SparkPost - Your application's emails:
       Delivered on time and to the inbox.
     * [https://mautic.com/]Mautic - Mautic Marketing Automation. Build
       smarter campaigns - and build them faster - with marketing
       automation that's quick to learn, simple to use, and easy to
       iterate.

Self-Hosted Services

     * [https://mailtrain.org/]Mailtrain - Self Hosted Newsletter App
       Built on Top of Nodemailer.
     * [https://mautic.org/]Mautic - Mautic Marketing Automation. Build
       smarter campaigns - and build them faster - with marketing
       automation that's quick to learn, simple to use, and easy to
       iterate.

Workflows

     * [https://github.com/leemunroe/grunt-email-workflow]Lee Munroe's
       Grunt Email Design - A Grunt workflow for designing and testing
       responsive HTML email templates with SCSS.
     * [https://github.com/darylldoyle/Gulp-Email-Creator]Darylldoyle Gulp
       workflow - Gulp Email Creator is a gulp workflow inspired by Lee
       Munroe's grunt-email-design workflow.
     * [http://www.sitepoint.com/my-current-html-email-development-workflo
       w/]Html Email Development Workflow - A Typical Email Development
       Workflow by Sitepoint.

Articles

     * [http://www.leemunroe.com/email-design-workflow/]Email Design
       Workflow - An email design workflow by By Lee Munroe.

Design

     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/css/]CSS Support - A complete
       breakdown of the CSS support for every popular mobile, web and
       desktop email client on the planet.
     * [https://documentation.mailgun.com/best_practices.html#email-best-p
       ractices]Mail Servers Best Pratices - This guide is a brief summary
       of email best practices that we have learned from managing mail
       servers.
     * [http://stylecampaign.com/blog/2014/02/responsive-email-navigation/
       ]Stylecampaign - I looked at the navigation of 50 responsive retail
       emails. Here is a breakdown of the patterns I discovered.

Blogs

     * [https://litmus.com/blog/]Litmus Blog
     * [http://stylecampaign.com/blog/]Stylecampaign Blog
     * [http://myemma.com/content-hub]Myemma Blog
     * [http://blog.postmarkapp.com/]Postmarkapp Blog
     * [https://blog.spently.com/]Spently Blog
     * [http://www.emailmonks.com/blog/]Emailmonks Blog

Copy

     * [http://www.goodemailcopy.com/]Email Copy - Email copy from great
       companies.
     * [http://greatemailcopy.com/]greatemailcopy - A dose of well-crafted
       emails from around the web.

Resources

     * [http://email-toolbox.com/]Email toolbox - Hand-picked resources
       for email marketers and designers.
     * [http://mailchimp.com/resources/]Mailchimp - Super awesome
       resources from Mailchimp
     * [https://litmus.com/resources]Litmus Resources - Stay up to date
       with the latest email news and trends with Litmus resources.
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/resources/]Campaign Monitor
       Resources - Campaign Monitor resources will turn you into an expert
       in no time.
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/dev-resources/]Campaign Monitor
       Dev Resources
     * [http://templates.mailchimp.com/]Mailchimp - MailChimp Email Design
       Reference

Inspirations

     * [http://codepen.io/reallygoodemails/]Really good emails Codepen
     * [http://reallygoodemails.com/]Really good emails - The Best Email
       Designs in the Universe.
     * [http://milled.com/]Milled
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/best-email-marketing-campaigns/]Th
       e Top Email Campaigns -The most effective email marketing campaigns
       from Campaign Monitor.
     * [http://inspiration.mailchimp.com/#all]Mailchimp Inspiration -
       Mailchimp beautiful newsletters examples.
     * [http://htmlemaildesigns.com/]Htmlemaildesigns - Beautiful emails
       to help inspire your next email design.

Statistics

     * [http://myemma.com/brainiac/gate-free-stats]Myemma Email Stats - 18
       must-know stats for modern email marketers by Emma, Inc.
     * [http://mailchimp.com/resources/research/]Mailchimp Research -
       MailChimp's researchers are constantly analyzing data to help you
       make the most of your email campaigns.
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/resources/guides/email-marketing-n
       ew-rules/]Campaign Monitor 2015 Report - 2015 Report: The new rules
       of email marketing
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/company/annual-report/2016/]Campai
       gn Monitor 2016 Report - 2016 Report: Campaign Monitor 2016 Year in
       Review

Testing

     * [https://putsmail.com/]PutsMail - Free tool to test your HTML
       emails before sending them!
     * [https://litmus.com/]Litmus - Test and track your emails with
       Litmus
     * [https://www.campaignmonitor.com/testing/]Campaign Monitor - Test
       your design in all the different email client with Campaign
       Monitor.
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/grunt-litmus]Grunt Litmus - Send
       email tests to Litmus with grunt
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-litmus]Gulp Litmus - Send email
       tests to Litmus with gulp
     * [http://www.mail-tester.com/]SPAM mailtester - Test the Spammyness
       of your Emails
     * [https://mailtrap.io/]MailTrap - A Fake SMTP Server to Test, View
       and Share emails without spamming real customers.

Learning

     * [https://frontendmasters.com/courses/responsive-email/]Responsive
       HTML Email Design - Responsive email course by Justine Jand and
       Jason Rodriguez. They both work at Litmus.
     * [http://teamtreehouse.com/library/html-email-design]HTML Email
       Design - MailChimp UX Designer Fabio Carneiro demonstrates how to
       build a full-featured, mobile-friendly email from scratch.
     * [http://webdesign.tutsplus.com/series/mastering-html-email--webdesi
       gn-17696]Mastering HTML Email - This series of tutorials will take
       you through the fundamentals, exploring development techniques,
       workflow and design approaches.
     * [https://scotch.io/tutorials/building-responsive-email-templates-wi
       th-ink]Building Responsive Email Templates with Ink - Building
       Responsive Email Templates with Ink.
     * [https://litmus.com/community/learning]Litmus learning - Litmus
       learning resources.
